NK010(tha)026:0: phur ba rgyud lugs las bka' ma'i yan lag brgyad 'grel rgyud don gsal ba bzhugs /
NK010(tha)026:1: rgyal ba kun gyi gsang ba'i mdzod //
NK010(tha)026:2: rdo rje'i mtshon don la gnas pa //
NK010(tha)026:3: mi bskyod yang dag bde ba'i dngos //
NK010(tha)026:4: gsung gi rdo rje snying dbus bsten //
NK010(tha)026:5: de la snga 'gyur bka' ma'i gzhung las yan lag
NK010(tha)026:6: brgyad pa tshig don dbyings che ba zhig gsungs pa
NK010(tha)026:7: bka' gter gyi cho ga kun gyi sngon 'gror rgyu
NK010(tha)026:9: dang po phyag 'tshal ba'i yan lag ni /
NK010(tha)026:10: rdo rje slob dpon sangs rgyas dpal //
NK010(tha)026:11: dus gsum bzhugs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK010(tha)026:13: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi mchog tu mi
NK010(tha)026:14: 'gyur ba'i ye shes dam pa gang yin pa de
NK010(tha)026:15: ni kun rdzob kyi chos thams cad kyis mi phyed
NK010(tha)026:18: rdo rje mi phyed ces byar brjod //
NK010(tha)026:20: rnam 'joms las kyang mi chod pa /
NK010(tha)026:23: sra ba zhes sogs rdo rje'i chos bdun bstan pa yin no //
NK010(tha)026:24: de lta bu ni mtshon bya don gyi rdo rje'i
NK010(tha)026:25: ngo bo nyid yin pas sngags kyi gzhung lam kun
NK010(tha)026:26: la rdo rje'i theg pa dang /
NK010(tha)026:31: rdo rje'i dam tshig la sogs par grags pa las /
NK010(tha)026:32: de dag rnams kyi don ma nor bar rang gis
NK010(tha)026:33: gzigs pa'i phyir chos kyi ming gang zag la chags
NK010(tha)026:35: go 'phang de la gzhan yang bkri ba la mkhas pa'i slob dpon te /
NK010(tha)026:36: de lta bu'i bla ma ni sangs rgyas thams cad kyi bdag nyid yin cing /
NK010(tha)026:37: slob ma rang gi ngo gang nas sangs rgyas las
NK010(tha)026:38: kyang lhag cing bka' drin che bas dpal zhes phun
NK010(tha)026:39: sum tshogs pa'i ming gi cha nas smos pa ste
NK010(tha)026:41: ming dbang bskur ba'i dus kyang /
NK010(tha)026:42: dpal dang rdo rje'i sgra ldan par //
NK010(tha)026:44: de'ang rdo rje slob dpon ni dus gsum gyi sangs
NK010(tha)026:45: rgyas thams cad kyi ngo bo nyid yin pas thugs
NK010(tha)026:46: rje la bri gang med pa'i cha nas dus gsum
NK010(tha)026:47: bzhugs pa'i sgras rten de la phyag 'tshal ba ste
NK010(tha)026:49: phyag byar 'os pa bla ma'i rab //
NK010(tha)026:52: mchog gsum bsten pa'i zhing gyur la //
NK010(tha)026:53: gnyis med yid kyis skyabs su mchi //
NK010(tha)026:55: dkon mchog gsum po ni lam gyi gnas skabs na
NK010(tha)026:56: dad pas bsten zhing bsnyen par bya ba'i zhing sa
NK010(tha)026:57: bla na med pa yin la /
NK010(tha)026:58: skyabs su 'gro tshul gyi ngos nas tshogs zhing de
NK010(tha)026:59: dag gi spangs rtogs kyi yon tan rang rgyud la
NK010(tha)026:60: sgrub pa'i de kho na nyid rig pa'i stobs kyis
NK010(tha)026:61: skyabs su 'gro bas na gnyis med kyi sgra zhugs
NK010(tha)026:62: pa'o // 'di la ston pa'i zhing zhes 'dri ba ni nor ba chen po ste /
NK010(tha)026:64: sangs rgyas la ston par rung yang chos dang dge 'dun ston pa ma yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK010(tha)026:66: ston pa bla med sangs rgyas rin po che //
NK010(tha)026:67: skyob pa bla med dam chos rin po che //
NK010(tha)026:68: 'dren pa bla med dge 'dun rin po che //
NK010(tha)026:69: zhes pa 'di tsam gyis kyang dkon mchog gsum po'i byed las ngo shes par bya'o //
NK010(tha)026:71: dngos 'byor yid kyis rnam sprul pa'i //
NK010(tha)026:72: dag pa'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK010(tha)026:74: dngos 'byor ni bla na yod pa dang /
NK010(tha)026:75: yid sprul ni bla na med pa gnyis las /
NK010(tha)026:76: snga ma dngos rgyu dag pa dang /
NK010(tha)026:77: phyi ma byang chub sems dpa' kun tu bzang po'i
NK010(tha)026:78: mchod sprin dang mtshungs pa ting nge 'dzin rnam par
NK010(tha)026:79: dag pa'i stobs kyis 'bul bas dag pa'i mchod pa
NK010(tha)026:80: zhes bya'o // yan lag bzhi pa ni /
NK010(tha)026:81: dngos grub chu bo gcod pa'i gegs //
NK010(tha)026:82: nyes byas ma lus bshags par bgyi //
NK010(tha)026:83: zhes rdo rje theg pa'i lam nas ji ltar 'thob
NK010(tha)026:84: tu rung ba'i dngos grub rnam pa gnyis po gzugs
NK010(tha)026:85: can gyi rgyan du bkod nas /
NK010(tha)026:86: de lta bu'i dngos grub kyi chu bo gcod pa'i
NK010(tha)026:87: bgegs chen por gyur pa ni lus ngag yid gsum
NK010(tha)026:88: gyi sgo nas nyes par byas pa'i dam sdom nyams
NK010(tha)026:89: chag yin te / phur pa myang 'das las /
NK010(tha)026:90: de ltar dam la mi gnas na //
NK010(tha)026:91: sa bon me yis tshig pa yin //
NK010(tha)026:92: t+aa la'i shing ni mgo bcad bzhin //
NK010(tha)026:94: zhes pa ltar dam tshig nyams na bskyed rdzogs kyi
NK010(tha)026:95: lam la ci tsam 'bad kyang t+aa la'i shing gi
NK010(tha)026:96: mgo bcad pa ltar ji ltar 'bad kyang mi skye
NK010(tha)026:97: ba dang mtshungs pas stobs bzhi'i gnad la brten nas
NK010(tha)026:98: bshags pa'o // yan lag lnga pa ni /
NK010(tha)026:99: phyogs bcu 'khor gsum dag pa'i chos //
NK010(tha)026:100: ma chags spyod la rjes yi rang //
NK010(tha)026:101: 'di ltar shar la sogs pa'i phyogs bcu ni dmigs
NK010(tha)026:102: pa dang bcas shing phan tshun dang yan man gcig
NK010(tha)026:103: la gcig ltos kyis rjes dpags la brten nas blos
NK010(tha)026:105: so sor rtog pa'i shes rab zab mo'i phyogs rang
NK010(tha)026:106: bzhin med pa'i de kho na nyid khong du chud
NK010(tha)026:107: pa dang / de bzhin du bdag dang /
NK010(tha)026:109: gnyis kar dmigs pa'i 'khor gsum yongs su dag pa
NK010(tha)026:110: ni bden gnyis dbyer med du rtogs pa'i chos bla
NK010(tha)026:112: de'i ngang la ma chags par spyod /
NK010(tha)026:113: ma zhen par goms su 'jug pa ni don dam pa'i rjes su yi rang ba'o //
NK010(tha)026:115: dag pa'i mtha' bzhi dri ma med //
NK010(tha)026:116: rdzogs pa'i byang chub sems bskyed do //
NK010(tha)026:117: zhes pa 'di la 'grel tshul gnyis byas kyang rung ste /
NK010(tha)026:118: kun rdzob sems bskyed dang bstun na /
NK010(tha)026:119: tshangs pa'i gnas pa bzhi dag pa byang chub sems
NK010(tha)026:120: dpa' spyan ras gzigs kyi thugs rgyud la yod pa'i
NK010(tha)026:121: tshad med bzhi lta bu'i sgo nas rdzogs pa'i byang
NK010(tha)026:122: chub tu sems bskyed pa dang /
NK010(tha)026:123: don dam sems bskyed kyi dbang du byas na /
NK010(tha)026:124: yod med rtag chad kyi mtha' bzhi rnam par dag
NK010(tha)026:125: pa ni nges don dbu ma chen po dri ma
NK010(tha)026:127: de'i ngang du lam bden 'dus byas pa thams cad
NK010(tha)026:128: rdzogs pa'i byang chub chen por dmigs pa med pa'i
NK010(tha)026:129: sems bskyed pa'o // yan lag bdun pa ste /
NK010(tha)026:130: bde gshegs dbang phyug sems can la /
NK010(tha)026:131: dgos pa gsum phyir lus dbul lo //
NK010(tha)026:132: de la lus dbul ba 'di ni theg pa chen
NK010(tha)026:133: po'i sde snod gnyis las gsungs pa'i yon tan gyi
NK010(tha)026:135: gya nom pa ste 'byung ba lnga'i rdos pas bcings
NK010(tha)026:136: pa'i bdag 'dzin gyi phung po 'di phul bas bdag
NK010(tha)026:137: med rgyal ba'i zhing du sbyar ba'i dgos pa dang
NK010(tha)026:139: rkang pa dang po'i don gyi bde gshegs ni 'das pa'i sangs rgyas /
NK010(tha)026:140: dbang phyug gi da lta ba'i sangs rgyas bla ma /
NK010(tha)026:141: sems can ni ma 'ongs pa'i sangs rgyas bder gshegs
NK010(tha)026:142: snying po'i rang bzhin can gsum gyi tshogs zhing ngos
NK010(tha)026:143: bzung nas rkang pa gnyis pa'i don /
NK010(tha)026:144: 'das pa'i sangs rgyas la phul bas de dag gi
NK010(tha)026:145: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las mi zad pa
NK010(tha)026:146: rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i yon tan mngon du 'gyur ba'i
NK010(tha)026:147: dgos pa dang / da lta ba la phul bas
NK010(tha)026:148: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi ye shes dam
NK010(tha)026:149: pa'i snod du rung zhing dbang dang byin rlabs la
NK010(tha)026:150: brten nas 'bras bu thob pa'i dgos pa dang /
NK010(tha)026:151: ma 'ongs pa la phul bas theg pa chen po'i
NK010(tha)026:152: 'bras bu thob pa'i don po gzhan don mthar phyin
NK010(tha)026:153: pa'i rten 'brel 'grig pa ste dgos pa gsum dang
NK010(tha)026:154: ldan pa'i phyir na rdo rje las rim las /
NK010(tha)026:155: phyogs bcu sras dang bcas pa dang //
NK010(tha)026:156: dbang phyug sangs rgyas da lta bdag /
NK010(tha)026:157: ma 'ongs rang bzhin sems can la //
NK010(tha)026:158: dgos pa gsum phyir lus dbul bya //
NK010(tha)026:159: mchog gi yon phyir snod du 'gyur //
NK010(tha)026:161: snga rabs ba phal mo ches go ba ni blangs /
NK010(tha)026:163: bde gshegs dbang phyug sems can la //
NK010(tha)026:164: dag pa gsum gyi lus 'bul lo //
NK010(tha)026:165: bdag dang mtha' yas sems can rnams //
NK010(tha)026:166: dus gsum bzhugs la lus 'bul lo //
NK010(tha)026:167: zhes rgyud tshig 'chol ba grags pa shin tu brtan na'ang /
NK010(tha)026:168: rgyu mtshan med pa'i rtog dpyod tsam mo //
NK010(tha)026:170: tshe rabs bgrangs pa'i las rnams kun //
NK010(tha)026:171: bsdus te byang chub chen por bsngo //
NK010(tha)026:172: de la 'khor ba spyi tshan gyi thog ma /
NK010(tha)026:173: 'di tsam nas so zhes brjod par mi nus kyang /
NK010(tha)026:174: rang ngo la ltos na rgyu bdag nyid gcig pa'i ma rig pa ye ldan gyi tshul /
NK010(tha)026:175: rkyen lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pa dus mnyam gyi tshul /
NK010(tha)026:176: yul la kun tu btags pa'i ma rig pa phyis
NK010(tha)026:177: byung gi tshul gsum las tshe rabs kyi thog ma
NK010(tha)026:179: da ltar gyi bar du bgrangs pa'i bsam pa yid kyi las dang /
NK010(tha)026:180: sems pa lus ngag gi las la brten nas dkar
NK010(tha)026:181: po rnam par 'phel ba'i las ji snyed cig yod
NK010(tha)026:182: pa thams cad 'dir thabs la mkhas pa'i shes rab
NK010(tha)026:183: kyis bsdus te sems can thams cad rdzogs pa'i byang
NK010(tha)026:186: zhes pa'ang 'do khams pa las can gyi slob bu
NK010(tha)026:187: 'jigs med phrin las 'od zer gyis bskul ba las
